## Migration File Standards

### Naming Convention
```
<version>_<description>.sql
```
- 3-digit sequential version numbers (001, 002, 010, etc.)
- Lowercase with underscores for description
- One logical change per migration

### Required Header
```sql
-- =============================================================================
-- MIGRATION <number>: <Clear Title>
-- =============================================================================
-- Purpose: <One sentence describing what this migration does>
-- Breaking Change: Yes/No
-- Prerequisites: <Migration number> must be applied (if applicable)
-- =============================================================================
```

